DEPENDENCIES
============

yaposib depends on
- boost python http://www.boost.org
- coin osi https://projects.coin-or.org/Osi

BUILDING
========
o On GNU Linux:

- install COIN-OSI
- install boost-python
- modify src/Makefile according to your OSI installation
- cd src; make (to generate the shared library)
- at the root of the project, run 'python setup.py bdist_egg'
- install the egg generated in dist/ with easy_install

o On MS Windows:

Untested. Should work the same way. Testers, feedback is welcome.
